\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 You see and hear ads that talk about this being the most important election of our time\'85until the next election. \'a0In fact, I\'92ve had the privilege of voting for the past 24 years and I can\'92t remember an election where either side said\'85this ones not the important\'85just wait till the next one\'85\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 No there is fear, there is tension, there is real pain and frustration\'85and so what I want to do today as we enter into the last few days of this season of our country (hopefully for 4 more years) is take a moment and talk through how you deal with the election, how you pick a person, and how to deal with those that disagree with you\'85\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I know that\'92s a lot but I think we can do it today...\uc0\u8232 \
